            <div className="max-w-4xl mb-12 pt-4 px-6 md:pt-10 md:px-8 xl:pt-10 xl:px-0">
              {activeMainTab === 0 && (
                <>
                  <h3 className="text-[14px] md:text-[16px] font-medium! text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    A curated snapshot of the customer's world – their current context and operating model, board-level priorities, and emerging challenges with cost of inaction analysis.
                  </h3>
                  <p className="text-[15px] lg:text-[16px] text-white font-medium! leading-relaxed">
                    News, blogs, press releases, earnings calls, financial reports, exec interviews, market trends, competitive landscape – all inform a structured layout of what matters most to set the stage for strategic intervention.
                  </p>
                </>
              )}
              {activeMainTab === 1 && (
                <>
                  <h3 className="text-[15px] lg:text-[16px] font-medium! text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    A targeted set of value opportunities tied to what the customer can realistically achieve with a new approach – from cost efficiencies and productivity gains to revenue acceleration and risk reduction.
                  </h3>
                  <p className="text-[15px] lg:text-[16px] text-white font-medium! leading-relaxed">
                    This is filtered through logic and reasoning based on your organization’s capabilities and offerings – leading to areas of potential impact, expected business outcomes, a tailored ‘first draft’ value hypothesis, and the metrics most likely to matter to key decision-makers.
                  </p>
                </>
              )}
              {activeMainTab === 2 && (
                <>
                  <h3 className="text-[15px] lg:text-[16px] font-medium! text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Your guide for turning the value narrative into a collaborative engagement with key stakeholders.
                  </h3>
                  <p className="text-[15px] lg:text-[16px] text-white font-medium! leading-relaxed">
                    Insight into persona-level ownership of the hypothesized problem and related initiatives, an ‘outside in’ business case, and questioning that sharpens your business case and earns credibility.
                  </p>
                </>
              )}
            </div>

